OL,3,CMan fighting insurance company two
OL,4,Cyears on from contracting dengue fever
OL,6,FA Jersey man has been battling an
OL,7,Finsurance company for more than two
OL,8,Fyears after contracting dengue fever
OL,9,Fon holiday in Jamaica.
OL,11,FPaul Soares, 43, developed flu-like
OL,12,Fsymptoms in October 2023, which
OL,13,Fdeteriorated whilst he was out for
OL,14,Fdinner with his partner.
OL,16,F"I turned round to my partner, and I
OL,17,Fsaid 'Look, I don't feel well at
OL,18,Fall'," Paul told ITV News.
