OL,3,CMan fighting insurance company two
OL,4,Cyears on from contracting dengue fever
OL,6,F"I pretty much straight away blacked
OL,7,Fout and had a seizure - my partner was
OL,8,Fquite panicked. I came to, and pretty
OL,9,Fmuch instantly again, I had another
OL,10,Fblackout and another seizure."
OL,12,FHe was rushed in the back of an
OL,13,Fambulance to a private hospital, where
OL,14,Fhe spent four days recovering.
OL,16,FPaul's insurance company, Aviva
OL,17,FInsurance Limited, accepted his claim
OL,18,Fand has so far reimbursed costs of up
OL,19,Fto #16,000.
