OL,3,CMan fighting insurance company two
OL,4,Cyears on from contracting dengue fever
OL,6,FHowever, Paul was surprised to
OL,7,Fdiscover that there is an outstanding
OL,8,Fpayment of more than $1,990 (#1,486).
OL,10,F"I continued to receive phone calls
OL,11,Fand emails directly from the ambulance
OL,12,Fprovider, and in March this year, the
OL,13,Fdebt collector letters began to come,"
OL,14,FPaul explained.
OL,16,F"I work in the financial services
OL,17,Findustry, so it doesn't really look
OL,18,Fgood for me."
