OL,3,CMan fighting insurance company two
OL,4,Cyears on from contracting dengue fever
OL,6,FHe said insurance companies have a
OL,7,Fbigger ethical responsibility to look
OL,8,Fafter their customers.
OL,10,F"To deal with this solely has been a
OL,11,Fhuge drain," Paul added. "There are
OL,12,Ftimes when you think you just want to
OL,13,Fgive up, but I can't do that because
OL,14,Fthere's a wider issue here."
OL,16,FIn 2024, insurers only paid out for
OL,17,F80% of claims on single-trip policies,
OL,18,Faccording to the Financial Conduct
OL,19,FAuthority in the UK.
