OL,6,FThis compares to 99% of claims for car
OL,7,Finsurance.
OL,9,FConsumer Group Which? has filed a
OL,10,Fsuper complaint with the regulator
OL,11,Fagainst travel insurance firms for
OL,12,Ffailing to deal with systematic
OL,13,Fproblems with home and travel
OL,14,Finsurance.
OL,16,FSam Richardson, Deputy Editor of
OL,17,FWhich? Money Magazine, said Paul is
OL,18,Fnot alone, and the use of third-party
OL,19,Fproviders is widespread.
