OL,3,CMan fighting insurance company two
OL,4,Cyears on from contracting dengue fever
OL,6,F"What we want to happen is for the
OL,7,Fregulator to urgently work with the
OL,8,Fgovernment to crack down on insurers
OL,9,Fthat are breaking the rules," Sam
OL,10,Fexplained.
OL,12,F"These problems have been going on for
OL,13,Fyears."
OL,15,FThe Financial Ombudsman Service has
OL,16,Fupheld Paul Soares' complaint and
OL,17,Finstructed the company to pay Mr
OL,18,FSoares #600 in compensation.
