OL,6,FA spokesperson from Aviva Insurance
OL,7,FLimited has apologised to Paul and
OL,8,Fadded that they have offered the
OL,9,Fcompensation advised by the Ombudsman.
OL,11,FThey stated: "This is a complex case,
OL,12,Finvolving several entities across the
OL,13,Fglobe, and we were first made aware of
OL,14,Fa debt collection letter in March 2025.
